Class AccountDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • AccountDatabase

  • public class AccountDatabase
extends java.lang.Object
    Array-based container class with an initial capacity of 5 and holds different account instances in Checking, Savings, or MoneyMarket. It will automatically grow the capacity by 5 if the database is full.
